"n. (尤指少女的)风度，举止 【英】 n. (尤指少女的)风度， 举止(behavior ; demeanor; bearing) 【记】 de+port(拿)+ment→ 拿出姿态→举止; 【同】 参考：comport(举动 ，表现) 【例】 She learnt good deportment when she was quite young. n. (好的)风度; 举止 = behavior = demeanor = bearing 【记】de, port拿一拿出姿态一举止 【参】comport(v 举止) 【记】port本身有举止，态度，姿势的意思 【相关】port 举止，态度，姿势；comport 举止；deport 举止 deportment (n.)  c.1600, from Middle French déportement, from déporter ""to behave,"" from Old French deporter (see deport (v.1))."
